parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause the brakes to fail, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potentially fires.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
brake pedal linkage hangs
rear brakes drag
heat and fire
automatic park brake set fails
vehicle slows down
and starts a fire under the motor home.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal linkage can cause the rear brakes to drag, leading to heat and fire, and potentially loss of control.
symptoms: Brake pedal linkage hangs
rear brakes drag
heat and fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic park brake switch can cause the vehicle to slow down and start a fire under the motor home, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: Automatic park brake set fails
vehicle slows down
and starts a fire under the motor home.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake pedal sinking can cause the brakes to fail, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
pumping of pedal a couple of times activates brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected engagement of the automatic park brake while driving can cause the vehicle to stop abruptly, leading to accidents, loss of control, and potential injuries.
symptoms: The automatic park brake engages while driving
the brake engages when the gear selector is in reverse and the vehicle is backing up
the vehicle stops abruptly regardless of speed
the emergency brake system fails to hold properly when engaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the vehicle to shut off while driving, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts off while driving
especially after hitting a bump in the road
the vehicle vibrates or shakes excessively
the engine stalls or dies.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear and front spring leaves can cause the vehicle to bounce excessively, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to a rollover accident.
symptoms: The vehicle bounces or oscillates excessively
especially when driving over bumps or rough roads
the vehicle feels unstable or like it will turn over.
